    "en": {
      "title": "Main suspect in Bastian Mawatha shooting killed in police confrontation",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The main suspect in the recent shooting incident at Bastian Mawatha in Pettah, in which a man was shot to death and another injured, has been shot dead by police during a shootout at Bemmulla.",
        "Police said the suspect who died in the exchange of gunfire was identified as a main accomplice of the notorious underworld gangster known as \u2018Ganemulla Sanjeewa\u2019",
        "They said the suspect fled in a motorcycle when police tried to apprehend him.",
        "However, the suspect opened fire at the policemen and when the policemen returned fire, the suspect reported to have died.",
        "A 30-year-old man died and another one was injured when unidentified men came in a motorcycle and shot at them at Bastian Mawatha, Pettah during broad daylight on May 30.(DSB)"
      ],
